
Build An App
============

1. Gathered your requirements: tables, forms, fields, field Types
2. Create your wireframe: https://www.invisionapp.com
3. Create a Spreadsheet for your SharePoint Site Columns and your data views
4. Create a Powershell Script to create your list with your Site Columns and list Views
5. Create the site where your App will reside
6. Deploy your PowerShell Script to create your list on the site you created in previous step
7. Create the App
8. If you have to change the Layout of your App created in previous step.
